name: Crystal-Clear_v1
description:
This model can generate images at 1600x704 with no highres upscaling required.

Use with Automatic1111 or InvokeAi on RunDiffusion where you can generate your favorite CIVITAI models.

This merge was created to achieve clear and unrivaled image quality, color and sharpness; no more blurry or foggy filter over your image.

Join Civitai-Crystal beta on discord!

Join RunDiffusion on discord!

EXTRA:

Most of the images are rendered at 768x1216 with NO HighRes Optimization and NO Upscaling of any sort. The faces were not adjusted in any way. These images are raw results. As you can see, the model handles the prompt very well even at large sizes.

VERSION 1b:

In overly colorful pictures some details get lost in the intensity. Toned down the color intensity a little for a clearer and crisper image. Also, there are now extra details in your renders when compared to the previous version of Crystal-Clear.

Try your LORAs through this model and post your results.

Feel free to compare with other models.

Don't forget to post your results!
